reviewText: This is a great video, they give you step by step instruction on techniques that are very helpful and great for someone who wants to enhance their makeup technique. I would say that the techniques displayed in the video are great for someone like me who has no experience or little experience in makeup. The techniques were very crisp, clean, and precise. I would recommend this video to anyone.

Love this dvd, me and my girls learned so much I even brought contacts for the first time and I'm 34. I been getting nothing but compliments since I bought and used step by step makeup, Eyerotic & step by step braiding and weaving braiding. I can look like a Diva when I want to. I'm Marvel my husband name keep comming up.
